item.description:
ROSALIA's MOTOMAMI album doesn't have a Dolby Atmos version, only 2 fanmades (mine and Jp7's). Even though he has shared his version, I decided to do my version in Dolby Atmos, some of you may know that I work with True Immersive and I hate that it doesn't feel like an immersive experience in Atmos. I have done my best to give an immersive experience in Atmos, then I worked again on the album but with True Immersive technology to give 2 points of view, the result of both is somewhat similar, with the differences that one is more accurate than the other and one is 5.1 JOC and the other Immersive stereo. I give credit to the author of the stems, I used some of them, others were separated with AI. Finally, I added 4 songs to replace the ones that are not on this Atmos edition album, which are: LLYLM, BESO, SAOKO (Alternative Edition) and MOTOMAMI (Alternative Edition).
